{"title":"刘公岛〔外一首〕","authors":["刘国藏"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":11,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘公岛〔外一首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘国藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葱郁刘公岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉重受伤心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧海举明珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝母泪一樽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙境遭玷污，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辱恨悬国门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂涛裂岸炮隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨打故垒血殷殷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鏖战惊天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捐躯泣鬼神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪叠翻阅教科书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声呼唤“邓大人”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠碑如剑刺苍穹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不屈不挠此誓信！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗顶炮台横空书——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义、实力相依存。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天尽头*"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东穷碧落天尽头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高丽扶桑一望收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始皇安在？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦桥依旧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千载悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙丹灵药何处求？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀龙须，赶荣成，上文登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三中”时雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化涛声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲雷鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风满情怀澎湃志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆鼓征程荡心胸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小康有路，天无尽头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来不是梦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天尽头，位于山东荣成市龙须岛东头海滨。因为山东省陆地之最东端故名。秦始皇东巡曾到此，现有“秦桥遗址”。传说秦始皇派人东去采长生不老药即由此出发。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}